# DebateX Project Report: Architecture, Deliberation Pipeline, API & Tech Stack

DebateX is a self-hosted, multi-LLM deliberation system designed to produce high-confidence, synthesized responses to complex queries. It implements a structured multi-stage debate protocol using a council of diverse language models and an orchestrating Moderator (Chairman).

---

## 🏗️ System Architecture

DebateX employs a decoupled dual-tier architecture consisting of a high-performance **FastAPI backend** (Python) and a modern **React client** (Vite).

