## ⚡ API Reference

All endpoints are hosted on `http://localhost:8001` (to prevent collision with common local servers).

### REST Endpoints

#### Health Check
*   **Method**: `GET`
*   **Path**: `/`
*   **Response (JSON)**: `{"status": "ok", "service": "DebateX API"}`

#### List Conversations
*   **Method**: `GET`
*   **Path**: `/api/conversations`
*   **Response**: Array of metadata lists (newest first, filters out empty conversations).

#### Create Conversation
*   **Method**: `POST`
*   **Path**: `/api/conversations`
*   **Response**: `{"id": "uuid-string", "created_at": "timestamp", "title": "New Conversation", "messages": []}`

#### Get Conversation
*   **Method**: `GET`
*   **Path**: `/api/conversations/{id}`
*   **Response**: Complete history object.

#### Rename Conversation
*   **Method**: `PUT`
*   **Path**: `/api/conversations/{id}`
*   **Body**: `{"title": "New Title"}`

#### Delete Conversation
*   **Method**: `DELETE`
*   **Path**: `/api/conversations/{id}`

---

### Server-Sent Events (SSE) Stream
*   **Method**: `POST`
*   **Path**: `/api/conversations/{id}/message/stream`
*   **Request Body**: `{"content": "User prompt content"}`
*   **Header**: `Content-Type: text/event-stream`

The stream yields data lines (`data: { ... }`) indicating stage progressions and payloads:

| SSE Event Type | Payload Data | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| `stage1_start` | `{}` | Initial answers collection begins. |
| `stage1_complete` | `{"data": [{"model": "...", "response": "..."}]}` | Emitted with all initial answers. |
| `stage2_start` | `{}` | Anonymized peer reviews begin. |
| `stage2_complete` | `{"data": [...], "metadata": {"label_to_model": {...}, "aggregate_rankings": [...]}}` | Emitted with evaluations and sorted rankings. |
| `round3_start` | `{}` | Revise or defend round begins. |
| `round3_complete` | `{"data": [{"model": "...", "decision": "REVISE/DEFEND", "response": "..."}]}` | Emitted with revisions or defense explanations. |
| `round4_start` | `{}` | Challenger critique round begins. |
| `round4_complete` | `{"data": {"model": "...", "response": "...", ...}}` | Emitted with target and critic content. |
| `stage3_start` | `{}` | Chairman synthesis starts. |
| `stage3_complete` | `{"data": {"model": "...", "response": "..."}}` | Emitted with final synthesized master response. |
| `title_complete` | `{"data": {"title": "..."}}` | Emitted with generated chat title. |
| `complete` | `{}` | Deliberation saved, stream closes. |
| `error` | `{"message": "..."}` | Stream aborted due to a fatal error. |

